FBIS4-1389 "drafr082_c_94003" FBIS-AFR-94-082 Daily Report 27 Apr 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA 18 Reported Injured 18 Reported Injured MB2704071694 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in English 0700 GMT 27 Apr 94 MB2704071694 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network English BFN [Text] Eighteen people have been injured, at least six of them seriously, in this morning's explosion at Jan Smuts Airport in Johannesburg. The blast occurred on the second floor of the international arrivals hall, causing extensive damage to the interior of the building. Several windows were blown out and the ceiling collapsed.
